      "number": 25,
      "question": "先天性甲狀腺功能低下症(congenital hypothyroidism)若區分為甲狀腺發育不全(dysgenesis)及合成異常 (dyshormonogenesis)兩大類病因,下列那一選項的致病病因與其他三者最不相同?",
      "options": {
        "A": "Pendred syndrome",
        "B": "lingual thyroid",
        "C": "iodide transport defect",
        "D": "iodide organification defect"
      },
      "answer": "B"
    },
