      "stage_id": 0,
      "number": 2,
      "question": "35 歲男性於健檢時發現血尿(hematuria)。 門診再追蹤尿液檢查發現:蛋白排泄量(protein excretion) 1500 mg/day、10~20 RBCs/HPF、dysmorphic RBC (+)、RBC cast (+)。後續安排下列評估,何者最不適當?",
      "options": {
        "A": "檢測免疫血清學檢查,例如complement levels(C3, C4)、cryoglobulins、anti-GBM antibody、ANCA、 ASLO、VDRL、HIV",
        "B": "測B 型肝炎(hepatitis B)、C 型肝炎(hepatitis C)病毒血清學檢查",
        "C": "靜脈腎盂造影(intravenous pyelography)或逆行性腎盂攝影(retrograde pyelography)",
        "D": "腎臟超音波(renal ultrasonography),必要時考慮腎臟切片(renal biopsy)檢查"
      },
      "answer": "C"
    },
