        "D": "根據NET 腫瘤細胞的分化程度可分成low grade(G1)、intermediate grade(G2)及high grade(G3)。 一般將G1 稱為well-differentiated NET,G2 及G3 稱為poorly-differentiated NET"
      },
      "answer": "A",
