      "stage_id": 0,
      "number": 27,
      "question": "12 歲男童,因發燒與咳嗽4 天就診,診斷為非典型肺炎,並給與azithromycin 10 mg/kg/day QD 3 天治 療。治療後一天隨即退燒,兩次抽血檢驗Mycoplasma pneumoniae 的IgG 與IgM 抗體均為陰性。下列何者是 最可能的病原?",
      "options": {
        "A": "Streptococcus pneumoniae",
        "B": "Chlamydia trachomatis",
        "C": "Chlamydia pneumoniae",
        "D": "Mycoplasma hominis"
      },
      "answer": "C"
    },
    {
      "id": "115020_1_28",
      "roc_year": "115",
